## Welcome to Technology Insights by Chris Zenzel

Hello and welcome to my blog on technology insights. My name is Christopher Zenzel. I am 23, a Systems Engineer, developer of smart technology applications, a fan of Disney, especially Frozen, freemason, noble, and a lot more!
